OL,6,FWATCH: A man threatened A&E staff in
OL,7,FBrighton with a knife before being
OL,8,Ftasered by police.
OL,10,FA man who threatened hospital staff
OL,11,Fwith a knife during an incident in
OL,12,FAccident and Emergency in Brighton has
OL,13,Fbeen jailed for five years.
OL,15,FJoshua Byrne had attended the Royal
OL,16,FSussex County Hospital on Tuesday 3rd
OL,17,FOctober in the day for treatment.
OL,19,FThe 32-year-old was later seen outside
OL,20,Fthe A&E department during a fire alarm
OL,21,Fafter he had been discharged.
