OL,6,FAfter arguing with security at around
OL,7,F11pm, Byrne became irate and entered
OL,8,FA&E, threatening staff and members of
OL,9,Fthe public.
OL,11,FCCTV from inside the hospital shows
OL,12,Fhim lunge towards a security guard and
OL,13,Fshouting "I will stab you in the face".
OL,15,FHe took a mobile phone from a patient
OL,16,Fby force, and narrowly missed stabbing
OL,17,Fa nurse.
OL,19,FMultiple calls were made to the police
OL,20,Fand officers arrived at the scene
OL,21,Fwithin minutes.
