OL,6,FTwo officers from Sussex Police, PC
OL,7,FGreg Devlin and PC Max Setra, used a
OL,8,Ftaser to safely arrest Byrne.
OL,10,FHe later told police that he carries a
OL,11,Fknife because he stole thousands of
OL,12,Fpounds from an Albanian drug dealer
OL,13,Fand felt the need to carry a knife
OL,14,F"for protection".
