OL,6,FAt Lewes Crown Court on February 20,
OL,7,FByrne admitted attempting to cause
OL,8,Fgrievous bodily harm with intent,
OL,9,Fthreatening a person while in
OL,10,Fpossession of a bladed article in a
OL,11,Fpublic place, and affray.
OL,13,FByrne, unemployed of Ingram Crescent
OL,14,FEast, Hove, was sentenced to five
OL,15,Fyears in prison, which includes an
OL,16,Fextended licence period for a further
OL,17,Fthree years.
