OL,6,FHer Honour Judge Christine Laing KC
OL,7,Fpraised the bravery and
OL,8,Fprofessionalism of the hospital staff
OL,9,Fand security guards, and the RPU
OL,10,Fofficers who detained Byrne.
OL,12,FIn particular, the hospital staff who
OL,13,Fkept calm under pressure and escorted
OL,14,Fpatients and members of the public to
OL,15,Fsafety, and protected other patients
OL,16,Fcould not be moved during the incident.
OL,18,FDivisional Commander Chief
OL,19,FSuperintendent Rachel Carr said: "The
OL,20,Factions of the hospital staff and
OL,21,Fsecurity was incredible that night.
