OL,6,F"It was a distressing incident for
OL,7,Feveryone in the hospital, but the
OL,8,Fstaff's professional actions ensured
OL,9,Fvulnerable patients were protected.
OL,11,F"Byrne's actions were highly reckless,
OL,12,Fputting his own safety and the safety
OL,13,Fof everyone else at risk.
OL,15,F"He was swiftly arrested, and we are
OL,16,Fpleased that a dangerous criminal has
OL,17,Fnow been sentenced."
