OL,11,FChief Inspector Simon Yates, said: "We
OL,12,Fknow that there is increased concern
OL,13,Ffrom the public about knife crime.
OL,15,F"Stories in the media and social media
OL,16,Fcan increase these concerns, and can
OL,17,Flead some individuals to arm
OL,18,Fthemselves with a knife in a misguided
OL,19,Fattempt to protect themselves.
