OL,6,F"Sadly it is becoming commonplace for
OL,7,Fpolice officers to encounter weapons
OL,8,Fsuch as hunting knives and concealed
OL,9,Fweapons which have been purchased
OL,10,Fonline, with few, if any, checks to
OL,11,Fprevent them being used in crime.
OL,13,F"We know that knife crime can destroy
OL,14,Fthe lives of those impacted, their
OL,15,Ffamilies and loved ones, and our
OL,16,Fcommunities.
